description: Prince Emanuele Filiberto de Savoia, the grandson of the last remaining king of Italy, has teamed with the acclaimed Milan-born Chef Mirko Paderno to provide LA with a royal taste of fresh and authentic Italian cuisine. Everything from this regal truck is crafted with the highest quality ingredients, from the flour, olive oil, and truffles imported directly from Italy, to the organic produce sourced from local Southern California farms. Each pasta dish is made fresh to order and topped with scrumptious handmade sauces, all for optimal deliciousness that you’re sure to savor. Decadent desserts include Tiramisu and Panna Cotta. This noble yet affordable gourmet fare is undoubtedly a local favorite and if you wish to charm your guests with unforgettable flavors and fun, you must have Prince of Venice come cater your next affair.
name: Prince of Venice Food Truck
